  "message": "Update verification matrix and add CVE arena trial results for bd-qwm\n\nThe conformance verification matrix gains updated pass/fail accounting\nacross strict and hardened modes. New CVE arena results from the bd-qwm\ntrial batch capture fixture_startup, strict, and hardened run outputs\nacross three separate test executions (2026-03-04), providing\nregression baseline data for future interposition correctness checks.\n\n- tests/conformance/verification_matrix.json: updated test outcome\n  counts and status classifications\n- tests/cve_arena/results/bd-qwm/: raw trial outputs (fixture_startup,\n  strict.stderr/stdout, hardened.stderr/stdout) plus trace.jsonl and\n  artifact_index.json for three runs\n- .beads/issues.jsonl: issue tracker sync\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
