lands.\"\n+        \"notes\": \"Phase-0 startup ABI skeleton and invariant pipeline are implemented and unit-covered. Remaining closure blocker: controlled fixture binary still times out under LD_PRELOAD in strict+hardened mode (2026-03-04 evidence run_id=20260304T024556Z).\"\n       }\n     },\n     {"
